# Typography Standards

- Primary UI font is `Roboto`.
- Default body copy uses normal weight (`400`).
- Use medium weight (`500`) for headings, labels, and controls.
- Use bold (`700`) only for intentional emphasis (critical values, high-priority headings).

## Do

- Preserve clear visual hierarchy via size and spacing first, then weight.
- Keep text readable with strong contrast on light surfaces.

## Don't

- Do not set broad containers or entire pages to bold.
- Do not mix many font families unless explicitly approved in design docs.
